  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV20">
<l>ciṉmoḻi nōyō kaḻiperun teyvamin nōyiṉateṉ</l>
<l>ṟiṉmoḻi kēṭku miḷanteyva maṉṟitu vēlaniṉṉī</l>
<l>yeṉmoḻi kēṇmiṉeṉ ṉammaṉai mīrula kēḻumuṇṭāṉ</l>
<l>coṉmoḻi mālaiyan taṇṇantu ḻāykoṇṭu cūṭṭumiṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The pain of her with few words, it is much [due to] the great god. It is not of the young god</l>
<l>who listens to sweet words: “this pain is thus”. Stop, spear-bearer!</l>
<l>Listen to my words, my mothers, with a word garland speaking</l>
<l>of him  who ate all the seven worlds, with pretty cool Tulsi adorn [her].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
